Package org.jamwiki.model

Provides basic objects for use on the Wiki, including WikiUser, Topic, TopicVersion, etc.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Category
    Provides an object representing a Wiki category.
    GroupMap
    This class is a container for managing groups and their members.
    ImageData
    Class for image and other data storing and loading.
    Interwiki
    Provides an object representing an interwiki link record.
    LogItem
    Provides an object representing a Wiki log entry.
    Namespace
    Namespaces allow the organization of wiki topics by dividing topics into groups.
    RecentChange
    Provides an object representing a Wiki recent change.
    Role
    Provides an object representing a Wiki role that can be extended by the specific security implementation.
    RoleMap
    Provides an object representing a mapping of a user or group to a set of roles.
    SearchResultEntry
    Provides an object that can be used to store search result information.
    Topic
    Provides an object representing a Wiki topic.
    TopicVersion
    Provides an object representing a version of a Wiki topic.
    UserBlock
    Provides an object representing a user block.
    VirtualWiki
    Provides an object representing a virtual wiki.
    Watchlist
    Provides an object representing a watchlist object consisting of a virtual wiki and a collection of topics being watched.
    WikiConfigurationObject
    Provides an object representing a configuration value as used by WikiConfiguration.
    WikiFile
    Provides an object representing a file uploaded to the Wiki.
    WikiFileVersion
    Provides an object representing a version of a file uploaded to the Wiki.
    WikiGroup
    Provides an object representing a Wiki group.
    WikiImage
    Provides an object representing a Wiki image.
    WikiReference
    Provides an object representing a Wiki reference, which is a citation appearing within a Wiki topic.
    WikiUser
    Provides an object representing Wiki-specific information about a user of the Wiki.
    WikiUserDetails
    Model representing user login details.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TopicType
    Allowable type values for topics.
